      <p begin="00:46:12,162" end="00:46:14,573">- Weet je, niemand knipte haar zo.</p>
      <p begin="00:46:14,573" end="00:46:18,135">Ik bedoel, jij knipte haar<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>zoals wij stof knippen.</p>
