      <p begin="00:49:44,798" end="00:49:45,850">De hele essentie.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:45,850" end="00:49:48,697">De opwinding van onze creativiteit.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:48,697" end="00:49:52,958">En ik zeg "onze" <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>want het is altijd teamwork.</p>
