      <p begin="00:50:30,719" end="00:50:31,593">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:50:31,593" end="00:50:33,031">- Dus dan, open je een academie.</p>
      <p begin="00:50:33,031" end="00:50:33,959">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:50:33,959" end="00:50:35,748">En dan komen ze van <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>vele verschillende landen.</p>
